31
00:01:40,710 --> 00:01:41,550
Do I qualify

32
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,480
to interrogate you?

33
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:46,760
Your Highness, you're imperial nobility.

34
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,200
Of course you do.

35
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,400
To tell you the truth,

36
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,430
I had no intention of sparing you.

37
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,640
But Lu Chang advised me,

38
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,070
saying that you're merely

39
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,430
a disposable pawn in this game.

40
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:02,000
The true culprit lies behind you.

41
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,350
That's why I agreed

42
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,560
to give you a chance to live.

43
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:08,280
Do you mean it?

44
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,430
My word is bond.

45
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,960
Believe it or not.

46
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:14,360
But you should know

47
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,800
the Jian Family's case implicates dozens,

48
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,470
and Su Changhua's embezzlement

49
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,750
involves hundreds of lives.

50
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,360
The crimes warrant clan extermination.

51
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,800
You might as well

52
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,590
weigh your own worth

53
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,960
and see if you can bear the consequences.

54
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:43,870
Gao Shicai,

55
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,590
just tell us

56
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,080
if Prince Yu

57
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,520
instructed you to do this.

58
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,920
How do you know?

59
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:56,150
During Su Changhua's tenure in Jianglin,

60
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:58,590
he secretly investigated some local officials.

61
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,310
They embezzled, perverted the law,

62
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,560
and exploited the people,

63
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,120
yet evaded justice due to their

64
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,590
powerful networks and factional alliances.

65
00:03:08,910 --> 00:03:10,280
Without exception,

66
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,680
they opposed the reforms.

67
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:17,360
His Majesty hesitated to initiate reforms,

68
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,800
even banning discussions about them.

69
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,750
If Su had reported how the officials

70
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,960
exploited loopholes in the old system

71
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:27,190
and undermined the state's integrity,

72
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,710
His Majesty would've recognized its flaws.

73
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:32,870
