74
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:36,560
forcing His Majesty to commit to reform.

75
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,000
As a defender of the old system,

76
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,960
Prince Yu wouldn't stand by.

77
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:47,190
He must eliminate Su to smother

78
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:51,190
any chance of the reforms' revival.

79
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,680
Before Su died,

80
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,710
he entrusted the evidence

81
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,000
of the officials' crimes to Jian Jinhai.

82
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:01,310
That's why the Jian Family was massacred.

83
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:05,080
When you failed to find the evidence,

84
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,560
you relentlessly hunted and tried to

85
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,150
wipe out Jian Jinhai's daughter,

86
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:11,150
Jian Mingshu.

87
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:14,190
Your account is flawless.

88
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:17,480
No wonder a prized disciple of Su Changhua.

89
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:20,560
Do you know the identity of the black-cloaked

90
00:04:20,850 --> 00:04:22,070
masked assassin who tried to kill you?

91
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,560
I don't know his true identity.

92
00:04:24,670 --> 00:04:25,510
I only know

93
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:27,360
he is deeply trusted by Prince Yu.

94
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:31,000
He relayed Prince Yu's every order.

95
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:33,680
The massacre and Jian Mingshu's assassination

96
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,000
were all his doing.

97
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,200
Your Highness,

98
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,000
I've told you everything.

99
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,000
Would you

100
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,560
spare my life?

101
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,310
Gao Shicai,

102
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,560
are you trying to negotiate with me?

103
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:58,950
Show your bargaining chips.

104
00:04:59,650 --> 00:05:01,750
Su Changhua took up the position of prefect

105
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:03,160
in order to gather evidence

106
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,750
of Prince Yu's faction's corruption.

107
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:06,920
When Prince Yu learned of this,

108
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:09,920
he ordered me, Wei Xian, and Lu Zegang

109
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:12,510
to frame Su for embezzling relief funds.

110
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:15,000
He also coerced Clerk Liu

111
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:17,000
into false testimony to ensure Su's death.

112
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,270
We've survived the officialdom this long.

113
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,390
We know once the birds are killed,

114
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:22,360
the bow will be put away.

115
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:25,310
How could we not take any precautions?

116
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,480
Do you have evidence against Prince Yu?

117
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,390
After His Majesty ordered

118
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,920
to reopen Su Changhua's case,

119
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:37,160
Wei Xian was killed.

120
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:40,680
Prince Yu clearly silenced him.

121
00:05:44,070 --> 00:05:45,160
Where is the evidence?

122
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,840
Your Highness,

123
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:51,800
I aided the evildoer and framed the upright.

124
00:05:51,930 --> 00:05:53,160
I deserve to die.

125
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:56,360
But my family knew nothing.

126
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,800
They're innocent.

127
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,630
Your Highness,

128
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,560
please spare their lives.

129
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,040
I'll submit

130
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:05,950
to any punishment.

131
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,720
You are ruthless

132
00:06:08,010 --> 00:06:09,270
and have committed countless evils,

133
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,360
yet you care for your family.

134
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:14,710
Fine.

135
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,720
Testify against Prince Yu,

136
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:19,190
and I'll ensure their safety.

137
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,360
Thank you, Your Highness.

138
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:25,120
I have ledgers

139
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,600
documenting Prince Yu's embezzlement

140
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,310
of Jianglin's taxes and military supplies.

141
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:31,750
I hid them in the capital.

142
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:33,350
Moreover,

143
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,560
as far as I know,

144
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,360
Lu Zegang holds

145
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,720
critical evidence on Su Changhua's case.

146
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:41,680
He's long wished to defect to Your Highness.

147
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:42,880
I,

148
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:45,310
I can persuade him to surrender the evidence.

149
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,760
Lu Chang,

150
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,560
keep Gao Shicai safe

151
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:50,800
and escort him to the capital in three days.

152
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,840
Yes.

153
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,880
Your Highness.

154
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,350
Reviewer Lu.

155
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:02,310
Prince Yu's influence

156
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:04,750
runs deeper than we imagined.

157
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:07,950
