158
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,750
After Jian Jinhai got the evidence,

159
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:14,310
he wrote to Lu Wenhan to appeal for justice.

160
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:16,560
But Lu Wenhan stood by

161
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,950
and watched Su Changhua die unjustly.

162
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:21,950
This proves

163
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,870
others in the court knew of the case,

164
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,120
not just us.

165
00:07:26,430 --> 00:07:28,920
But they all chose to keep silent,

166
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:30,830
fearing

167
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:32,000
Prince Yu's power.

168
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:49,590
Sir,

169
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,310
I didn't expect that after you passed away,

170
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,310
you left such a great help for me.

171
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:01,790
Lu Chang,

172
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:04,000
from this day forth,

173
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,190
will you join me in uncovering the truth

174
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:09,070
and restoring the reforms?

175
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,870
Born of humble origin,

176
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,270
I've seen the suffering of every class.

177
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,480
Our realm's

178
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,070
apparent peace

179
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,920
masks internal decay, external threats,

180
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,160
and numerous drawbacks,

181
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:24,750
all festering under the outdated system.

182
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:28,360
Without swift reform to correct this course,

183
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:32,080
the nation's foundations will crumble.

184
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:34,910
Thus, the reforms are vital.

185
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,960
I pledge my utmost to aid Your Highness

186
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,200
in implementing the reforms,

187
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:43,600
to honor my late mentor's spirit

188
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,960
and pacify the people's hearts.

189
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,150
Even if it costs my life,

190
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,790
I will never waver.

191
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:02,600
You're the right-hand man Mr. Su left to me.

192
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,240
Together, we'll face

193
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,120
whatever comes

194
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,360
without fear.

195
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,550
The case has progressed,

196
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:21,550
yet you're frowning.

197
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,150
What's happened now?

198
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:26,960
According to Gao Shicai,

199
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,870
Lu Wenhan could've aided my mentor,

200
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:32,790
but he chose to stand by.

201
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,030
The court

202
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:36,910
is full of bystanders

203
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:39,320
clinging to self-preservation.

204
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:40,350
Moreover,

205
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,870
you haven't acknowledged your blood ties.

206
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,510
Don't dwell on it.

207
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:45,360
But his inaction

208
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,150
led to Jian Jinhai's death indirectly.

209
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,480
After all, he's my biological father.

210
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:53,550
When we return to the capital,

211
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,960
