213
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,150
In my opinion,

214
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,510
she's much more clear-headed than you.

215
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,150
If she learns of this,

216
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:06,000
she'll scorn

217
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,000
Director Lu,

218
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,870
but she won't blame you for it.

219
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,790
- But...
- Your care over-complicates things.

220
00:10:15,410 --> 00:10:16,210
All right,

221
00:10:16,250 --> 00:10:17,550
