222
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:19,390
Stop sulking or you'll spoil the fun.

223
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,440
Smile.

224
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:31,360
- Great!
- Bravo!

225
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,630
Wonderful!

226
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,870
One more time!

227
00:10:34,930 --> 00:10:37,130
Do it again!

228
00:10:37,130 --> 00:10:40,620
Great!

229
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,550
Before coming, I heard there would be

230
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:47,480
a night market on the Beginning of Summer.

231
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:50,630
Everyone from nobles to street vendors

232
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:52,120
flocks there.

233
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:54,120
I was wondering

234
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:56,000
what kind of grandeur it would be.

235
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:58,270
Now from what I can see,

236
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,360
it rivals the capital itself.

237
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:02,550
The water town has a gentle elegance,

238
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:04,240
distinct from the capital's

239
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,550
austere majesty.

240
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,400
Nice!

241
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,220
