254
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:45,960
Just go.

255
00:11:46,550 --> 00:11:47,390
Go.

256
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:53,510
What are you looking at?

257
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,800
Just the scenery

258
00:11:57,790 --> 00:11:58,720
in the distance.

259
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,670
I'll go talk to Qingzhao.

260
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,680
Qingzhao.

261
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:15,360
They're releasing sky lanterns over there.

262
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,720
Let's go and take a look.

263
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,080
Sure.

264
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,350
Let's go.

265
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,000
What's happening?

266
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,800
Take care, folks.

267
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:34,630
Hello,

268
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,960
care to buy a sky lantern?

269
00:12:36,060 --> 00:12:37,240
Today is the Beginning of Summer.

270
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:39,000
Write your wishes on a lantern,

271
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,790
and they'll come true.

272
00:12:41,150 --> 00:12:42,120
Let's buy one.

273
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,800
Ok.

274
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:49,900
(Carefree)

275
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:54,060
(Carefree and Joyful)

276
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:58,420
(Safe and Sound)

277
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:00,800
Mingshu,

278
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:03,030
may your days be carefree

279
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:04,790
and filled with peace and joy.

280
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:08,510
May we remain true companions,

281
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:10,150
sharing safety year after year.

282
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:19,660
(Carefree and Joyful)

283
00:13:19,660 --> 00:13:22,580
