00:13:45,870 --> 00:13:47,150
I have something to tell you.

287
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:50,710
Mingshu.

288
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:53,590
Mingshu,

289
00:13:54,110 --> 00:13:56,200
there are more interesting spots.

290
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,670
Let's explore elsewhere.

291
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,870
For years,

292
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:02,030
I've dreamed of a man in a black robe.

293
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,320
In my dream,

294
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:07,150
I'm attracted to him,

295
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,000
but I don't know who he is.

296
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:14,120
Since you wear black robes too,

297
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,360
so I...

298
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,320
So,

299
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,200
you mistook me for that black-robed man

300
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,870
from your dreams?

301
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,670
You've always been kind,

302
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:34,270
and I cherished our time together.

303
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:39,790
I thought it might be love,

304
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:43,150
but as we've spent more time together,

305
00:14:43,550 --> 00:14:45,200
I've realized that it's not romantic.

306
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:47,590
Mingshu,

307
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:51,390
we've been through so much together.

308
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,750
I can feel your care and concern.

309
00:14:57,550 --> 00:14:59,390
How can our true feelings

310
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,150
mean less

311
00:15:02,150 --> 00:15:04,270
than some illusory dream?

312
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:05,800
The dream

313
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,790
may be illusory,

314
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:10,550
but feelings don't lie.

315
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:12,750
Now I know

316
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:14,630
who I'm really drawn to,

317
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:15,520
so I...

318
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,390
Mingshu,

319
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:18,350
don't say it.

320
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,280
You

321
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,870
just give me some more time.

322
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:22,720
I didn't realize

323
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:24,270
we had wandered so far.

324
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,080
Are you tired?

325
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,750
How about I carry you?

326
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:37,870
Really?

327
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,280
Hop on.

328
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,150
So beautiful!

329
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:02,910
But none compare to my wifey.

330
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:05,160
What did you call me?

331
00:17:06,270 --> 00:17:07,110
Wifey.

332
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:08,390
That's how

333
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:10,160
husbands here address their wives.

334
00:17:11,110 --> 00:17:12,790
Then what should I call you?

335
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,000
Hubby?

336
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:16,480
Hubby.

337
00:17:18,110 --> 00:17:19,480
Wifey, keep it serious.

338
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,350
People will laugh at me.

339
00:17:21,350 --> 00:17:22,350
Why?

340
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:24,030
Isn't this normal

341
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:25,200
for spouses?

342
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:42,160
I wish all the people of Da'an

343
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:43,720
could live in peace and prosperity.

344
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:46,680
My wifey's wish

345
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:48,920
is mine.

346
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:52,790
Every soul

347
00:17:53,310 --> 00:17:54,680
has loved ones behind them.

348
00:17:55,830 --> 00:17:56,670
I'll

349
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,070
try my best

350
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,160
to seek well-being for all the people

351
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:02,310
and let them share peace and prosperity.

352
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,800
I wish to walk side by side

353
00:18:15,270 --> 00:18:16,200
with my wife

354
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,480
on this path.

355
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:49,160
Mr. Lu?

356
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:53,200
Why are you still in Jianglin?

357
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:03,350
You're here investigating the case,

358
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,960
so I'm waiting for the result.

359
00:19:06,830 --> 00:19:08,160
Did Gao Shicai

360
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:10,200
reveal the mastermind?

361
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:12,350
I told you,

362
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:13,920
this isn't your concern.

363
00:19:17,310 --> 00:19:19,070
It doesn't matter if you don't tell me.

364
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:22,510
When you take him to the capital,

365
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:25,270
you'll surely act against the mastermind.

366
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,270
By then,

367
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:29,510
I'll learn the truth regardless.

368
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:31,880
Then let me tell you something.

369
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:35,350
Prince Yu didn't help you kill Wei Xian

370
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,350
for your vengeance,

371
00:19:37,830 --> 00:19:38,960
but to use your hand

372
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,320
in silencing

373
00:19:43,270 --> 00:19:44,440
his loose ends.

374
00:20:01,270 --> 00:20:02,750
Thank you for telling me.

375
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:06,510
I shall take my leave.

376
00:20:49,310 --> 00:20:50,960
Did you not have a pleasant talk

377
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,590
with Lady Tangli?

378
00:20:52,830 --> 00:20:53,880
You don't know.

379
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:56,590
Ever since the Songling Academy case,

380
00:20:57,350 --> 00:20:58,750
she has defected to Prince Yu.

381
00:21:00,550 --> 00:21:02,880
I already told her

382
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,000
he is the mastermind.

383
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:07,270
I don't know what she'll do.

384
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,200
With her nature,

385
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:13,590
she'd brave danger without hesitation.

386
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:16,350
That's true.

387
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:22,000
But I can't reason with her anymore.

388
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:24,960
I just hope she chooses wisely.

389
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:27,750
Is Su Tangli

390
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:31,000
the young lady from Jianglin

391
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,440
you've pined for all this time?

392
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:33,800
No.

393
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:36,440
No?

394
00:21:37,310 --> 00:21:38,350
Then someone else?

395
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:45,680
Let me ask you something.

396
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:49,040
What?

397
00:21:49,830 --> 00:21:52,750
You said our families were deeply connected.

398
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,030
Does that mean

399
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:55,680
we were close?

400
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:58,960
I guess so.

401
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,350
And you were really clingy.

402
00:22:03,510 --> 00:22:05,000
Yong'an Alley is a rough place.

403
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:08,000
It's not for a precious young lady

404
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,110
like you to come.

405
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,750
Don't come again.

406
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:12,960
Where I go and where I don't go

407
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:14,270
is my own business.

408
00:22:14,270 --> 00:22:15,590
I have my considerations.

409
00:22:16,070 --> 00:22:17,720
Besides, I came to see Madam Zeng.

410
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:19,110
If she welcomes me,

411
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,590
no one can stop me.

412
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:24,400
You were not just clingy with me.

413
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:26,960
You pestered Mother to teach you embroidery.

414
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:30,110
I learned embroidery from Mother?

415
00:22:31,510 --> 00:22:33,030
Her skills are unmatched.

416
00:22:33,030 --> 00:22:34,400
Yet after all this time,

417
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:36,750
I'm not half as good?

418
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:40,160
Talent is innate.

419
00:22:41,070 --> 00:22:42,960
You just lack it here.

420
00:22:45,350 --> 00:22:47,350
Your explanation makes sense.

421
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:49,550
Then answer me,

422
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:51,550
if not

423
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:54,160
for Mr. Su's evidence,

424
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:56,400
would you still have sheltered me

425
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,480
when I fell off the cliff?

426
00:22:59,030 --> 00:22:59,870
Of course.

427
00:23:00,550 --> 00:23:01,390
Why?

428
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:06,000
I've told you before.

429
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:09,200
Your parents helped me.

430
00:23:10,030 --> 00:23:11,510
We grew up together.

431
00:23:12,270 --> 00:23:13,790
You're like a sister to me.

432
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:16,190
Is that all?

433
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,190
Well...

434
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:23,590
That's how things were back then,

435
00:23:27,070 --> 00:23:27,920
but...

436
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:31,160
But what?

437
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:35,680
But it's really getting late.

438
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:38,240
Shouldn't you go back and sleep,

439
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,400
my dear young lady?

440
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:44,480
Not yet.

441
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:49,200
Tomorrow, we're heading back to the capital.

442
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,480
Do you remember

443
00:23:52,110 --> 00:23:54,110
our last journey back?

444
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:56,830
Bandits on our heels,

445
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,920
peril at the inn,

446
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,640
we managed

447
00:24:01,510 --> 00:24:04,270
to survive through all the dangers.

448
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:08,680
Now it feels like a dream.

449
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:10,520
True.

450
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:13,350
It's like a dream.

451
00:24:15,110 --> 00:24:16,270
And that dream

452
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:19,070
has changed us both.

453
00:24:38,660 --> 00:24:41,940
(Residence of Duke of the State)

454
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:43,630
Father.

455
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:44,870
Mother.

456
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:50,840
Son,

457
00:24:52,070 --> 00:24:53,880
finally, you're home.

458
00:24:54,310 --> 00:24:55,680
You left in such a hurry.

459
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,960
You have no idea how worried I was.

460
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,280
Qingzhao,

461
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:04,110
Hanlin Academy hadn't approved your leave,

462
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,240
yet you ran off.

463
00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:08,400
I had to clean up your mess.

464
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,760
Tell me,

465
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:12,830
where are your discipline and manners?

466
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:16,590
Your reprimand is justified, Father.

467
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,110
I left with Prince Rui

468
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,270
in an emergency,

469
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:22,310
so I couldn't arrange formalities.

470
00:25:23,510 --> 00:25:24,510
I beg your forgiveness.

471
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:27,110
Enough.

472
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:29,120
Look

473
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,550
how dust-covered and weary he is.

474
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,480
Let him have a rest first.

475
00:25:35,310 --> 00:25:36,150
Fine.

476
00:25:37,110 --> 00:25:37,950
Today,

477
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:39,200
you get some rest early.

478
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,520
Tomorrow,

479
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:42,000
attend duty promptly.

480
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,520
I'm not tired.

481
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:45,750
A quick wash, and I'll depart.

482
00:25:46,590 --> 00:25:48,030
Why the haste?

483
00:25:48,350 --> 00:25:50,030
You must be starving.

484
00:25:50,310 --> 00:25:52,270
I'll make you your favorite Dongpo Stew.

485
00:25:52,520 --> 00:25:53,400
Wait here.

486
00:25:53,510 --> 00:25:54,440
Mother, don't bother.

487
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:56,240
I'm not hungry.

488
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,270
What do you think

489
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,440
is wrong with Qingzhao?

490
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:15,590
I feel like he's become a different man

491
00:26:15,590 --> 00:26:17,030
since his return.

492
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:19,550
Could something have happened?

493
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:24,160
At least he takes his duties seriously.

494
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:25,640
He gets that from me.

495
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:28,830
You're too fixated on your own affairs

496
00:26:29,270 --> 00:26:31,270
to notice your son's state of mind!

497
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:32,670
State...

498
00:26:34,350 --> 00:26:35,350
State of mind?

499
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:51,080
Young Master,

500
00:26:51,590 --> 00:26:52,430
are you ok?

501
00:27:16,310 --> 00:27:17,640
Get me a pouch.

502
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,240
I'll wear it close to my body.

503
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:24,830
You're so devoted to Lady Lu.

504
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:26,640
If she isn't heartless,

505
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:28,200
how could she not be moved?

506
00:27:32,790 --> 00:27:34,200
Love isn't about being moved.

507
00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:38,510
Mingshu's heart lies elsewhere.

508
00:27:40,550 --> 00:27:41,750
What can I do?

509
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:44,800
I'm clumsy with words

510
00:27:45,450 --> 00:27:46,550
and not good at consoling people.

511
00:27:47,350 --> 00:27:48,190
But I know

512
00:27:48,550 --> 00:27:49,750
you're a very, very good man.

513
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:51,680
Even without Lady Lu,

514
00:27:52,350 --> 00:27:53,640
you'll still get a worthy match.

515
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:56,920
I don't care about worthy matches.

516
00:27:58,750 --> 00:28:00,200
I only care about Mingshu.

517
00:28:03,310 --> 00:28:04,150
Young Master,

518
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:05,480
you...

519
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:08,680
I'm fine.

520
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:12,550
Don't tell Mother about this yet.

521
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:16,350
She cares about the marriage arrangement.

522
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:19,310
I don't want her to be upset.

523
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:23,750
We'll tell her

524
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:27,110
when the time's right.

525
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,070
Then, Young Master,

526
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,480
I'll fetch you a pouch.

527
00:29:06,180 --> 00:29:10,060
(Top Scholar Residence)

528
00:29:11,350 --> 00:29:12,190
Mother.

529
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:15,000
We're back.

530
00:29:26,550 --> 00:29:27,440
Mother.

531
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:33,080
Mingshu.

532
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,160
I'm sorry.

533
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:43,480
Why apologize?

534
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:45,760
You have no idea

535
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:48,240
how happy I am

536
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:51,200
to hear you call me Mother.

537
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:02,070
I've never told you this,

538
00:30:04,110 --> 00:30:05,070
but my

539
00:30:05,790 --> 00:30:06,960
greatest dream

540
00:30:07,350 --> 00:30:09,880
was to have a daughter like you.

541
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:11,790
These days,

542
00:30:12,270 --> 00:30:14,030
you've made my dream real.

543
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,400
I should thank you,

544
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:16,240
shouldn't I?

545
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:18,200
Mother, what are you talking about?

546
00:30:19,070 --> 00:30:20,480
You're the best mother,

547
00:30:21,350 --> 00:30:22,550
and you'll always be my mother.

548
00:30:25,750 --> 00:30:26,590
My sweet girl,

549
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,480
say no more.

550
00:30:29,750 --> 00:30:31,070
My heart aches for you.

551
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:35,070
We're family.

552
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:38,070
Between family,

553
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:40,640
we don't need to dwell

554
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:43,240
on gratitude or guilt. Understand?

555
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:50,040
Your path ahead

556
00:30:50,790 --> 00:30:51,920
may have

557
00:30:52,550 --> 00:30:54,310
twists and turns.

558
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:57,240
I may not be able to help much.

559
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,880
I just want you to know

560
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,920
that no matter how far you go,

561
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,550
if you ever look back,

562
00:31:07,350 --> 00:31:08,960
my eyes will always be on you.

563
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:19,070
Are you craving my cooking?

564
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:21,270
Name what you want,

565
00:31:21,270 --> 00:31:22,400
and I'll make your favorite.

566
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:27,270
You know, it's good

567
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:33,200
that you're back.

568
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:41,080
Mother.

569
00:31:46,660 --> 00:31:48,540
(Supreme Court)

570
00:31:48,550 --> 00:31:49,960
The escort of Gao Shicai

571
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,350
(Crystalline Integrity)
went smoothly,

572
00:31:51,350 --> 00:31:52,550
and nothing happened.

573
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,240
Has Prince Yu

574
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:56,070
chosen not to take action?

575
00:31:56,390 --> 00:31:57,680
Prince Yu acts perversely

576
00:31:58,110 --> 00:31:59,030
and is unpredictable.

577
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,510
Gao Shicai is an important witness.

578
00:32:01,640 --> 00:32:03,070
Prince Yu must have countermeasures.

579
00:32:04,860 --> 00:32:06,030
Keep Gao Shicai

580
00:32:06,510 --> 00:32:07,590
under maximum security

581
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,350
and prohibit any contact with him

582
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:10,520
